U.K. Councils to Increase Fees for Local Services, Times Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-17T00:38:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/u-k-councils-to-increase-fees-for-local-services-times-reports.html
Many large municipal councils in the
U.K. plan to increase service fees by up to 400 percent to
maintain services such as parking, garbage collection and
burials, as the national government has effectively frozen
council taxes, the London-based Times reported, citing its own
survey.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
